review_title: Best Priced phone on the market
reviews: So far this phone is great, I like the continuous updates regarding security and android updates. The build quality is awesome. The UI doesnt seem to have any bugs and the phone runs really smooth. Battery usually lasts roughly 3 days on full charge. Only downside of this phone is the lack of cases for it .
